		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I kinda disagree with the whole programming complexity talk. Even 4-way (or 8-way, or whatever) scrolling isn't significantly hard to implement (heh, I have rewritten my engine so many times that I can probably write down a whole scrolling engine on paper in a couple of hours!). I think that many other aspects of game programming are more complex than the scrolling.

		

