	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />One interesting consequence of upgrading to 2 way scrolling is there are certain configurations of platforms, which could "guide" the player to move a fair distance horizontally (in other words, forced to backtrack), which would be impossible to put in a 1 way scroller because they could get walled off by the leftmost side of the screen.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


